{"tid":1643301,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋果公司：反警地圖app違反規則已下架","createTime":"2019-10-10T05:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T06:17:21.000Z","uid":227392,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8f370a56227cb481fc0d2b584b9c50cffcca8be5","tid":1643301,"uid":227392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:27:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJrD6K7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJrD6K7.jpg&h=752a928d&s={SIZE}\" /></div> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》昨日(9日)發表評論，質疑蘋果公司淪亂港暴徒「幫兇」，批評app商店內有一款地圖，向本港示威者通報警方行蹤、便利違法活動。蘋果公司宣布，該應用程式違反公司規則已下架，並指出該程式被用作伏擊警察，以及被罪犯用作傷害市民。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果公司表示，很多本港客戶已聯絡公司，就有關該地圖事宜作查詢，公司立即作出調查後，發現該地圖已被用於危害執法人員和香港居民。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果跪低，要賺人仔。</span></span>"},{"pid":"567492fdb122ebde2c10293e23bf7eea5b92865f","tid":1643301,"uid":143542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"蘋果？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9991ff06be5aa620c3468399f52b57d1f40ac3","tid":1643301,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0681cf2a848f836a1401dbea2d9873f2f828db46","tid":1643301,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"2407219f490ea50cae7a5a43820fc8e41c11894d","tid":1643301,"uid":235025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03ed709fd9855ea2b1810ce0d422354ac12ee933","tid":1643301,"uid":93141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:35:10.000Z","msg":"又多粒chinazi核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89981d1ddc23bea37989ce24ec0ea0b39624bdbe","tid":